<h2>Overview</h2>
<p>The <code>ping</code> attribute on <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> elements sends background POST requests to one or more URLs when the link is clicked. The user navigates directly to the link's <code>href</code> destination while the tracking requests are sent asynchronously — no redirect delay, no JavaScript required.</p>
<p><strong>Applies to:</strong> <a href="/docs/elements/native/a/"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a></p>

